            <line><![CDATA[<i>Hit:</i>]]> 2d6 + 3 acid damage, and the target is covered by acid (save ends).</line>
            <line>While covered, a target is slowed and takes ongoing 5 acid damage.</line>
            <line><![CDATA[<i>Miss:</i>]]> 5 acid damage.</line>
         </block>
